text: Eungella is a township in Queensland, Australia, near a National Park of the same name. Eungella may also be refer to a number of places and animals ==Places== * Eungella Dam, a dam in Queensland, Australia * Eungella, New South Wales, a town in New South Wales, Australia ==Animals== * Eungella honeyeater * Eungella torrent frog * Eungella tinker frog * Eungella gastric brooding frog
